snippet.title: Touhou Multi Scroll Shooting. Game play trailer July 2019.
snippet.description:
The shooting game with dynamic camera. This game provide both of vertical scrolling and horizontal scrolling mode.

Download link for trial version 0.28.
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1T4FwPV4Oj_LRnxMl9_g18Mr6hDXpcRKy/view

Visit a developer's page here.
https://www.facebook.com/Skydash-studio-462437223835181/

Visit a store page here.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1125000/Touhou_Multi_Scroll_Shooting/

A song in this video is made by LENK64 (also known as Miki Hiroyuki)
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCr5QOjJIzkEjnIbJwGwi7TA
